{"tid":1395002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"現職公務員懇請8月5日配合不合作運動！","createTime":"2019-08-01T15:17:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T16:53:28.000Z","uid":260335,"like":110,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"f55ed29224cad9cb757909a50504b576c1ee313d","tid":1395002,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:17:08.000Z","msg":"朋友無acc 我代post <br />\n<br />\n首先多謝大家有耐性等到8月5號 集會造勢後罷工<br />\n大家對我地既期望實在受寵若驚<br />\n對於罷工 有幾樣無可否認既事實大家要知道<br />\n公務員總人數約18萬 扣除警犬3萬多隻<br />\n要發動有影響力既罷工 最少需要約20000<br />\n<br />\n而在我觀察 政府內部舊制太多藍絲 <br />\n其他守舊 就算支持 理解 都未必會響應<br />\n因為佢地只係想安安穩穩 report 唔花 拎埋旅遊津貼<br />\n然後退休<br />\n<br />\n而新制大約有9萬 當中約 大概1/5 係未過probation 當中絕大部份都係政治冷感 和理非等 <br />\n可以預期 真係會擺工既  人數不會多於10000 <br />\n而呢10000 當中 相信7成都只會係以sick leave <br />\nVocation leave <br />\n到8月6號 大家就會返工 對政府衝擊可想而知等於示弱<br />\n<br />\n今次罷工 <br />\n可以算係我地既底牌 所以想贏 惟有盡地一鋪<br />\n我在此懇請配合各種不合作運動 <br />\n<br />\n有好想人好想罷工 但家中有大有細 有層樓要供 <br />\n你唔能夠期待一個係社會做左野咁耐既人 <br />\n仲有年輕人呢顆赤子之心 <br />\n<br />\n所以 如果有一個情況 有一個藉口 <br />\n可以打電話同公司講 因為各種原因返唔到工<br />\n壓力就會細好多 <br />\n<br />\n你睇下8號波大家幾開心<br />\n香港人其實又點會鍾意返工？<br />\n只係需要一個明正言順返唔到工既理由<br />\n<br />\n至於民意 我長話短說 <br />\n百萬遊行 612勇武抗爭 梁烈士以死相諫 200萬人遊行 盧烈士既血字 圍攻立法會 義士逃亡海外<br />\n元朗白衫黑幫無差別襲擊  黑警無恥配合 <br />\n728 44位義士被控暴動 相中仲有好多歷歷在目既片段 同鮮血 大家都唔會忘記<br />\n<br />\n香港 一個我地引以為傲既國際大城市<br />\n回歸20年 我地仲可以走去既又有幾多？<br />\n今時今日都唔醒既人 永遠都唔會醒<br />\n會理解既人 一定會理解<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8QiQzsF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8QiQzsF.png&h=afcc7de6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXwyxem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXwyxem.png&h=61f3ba09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上係公務員群組既投票 <br />\n<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天佑我城"},{"pid":"7d9e3cf99b53a2079054db82fe754a2e5155fd37","tid":1395002,"uid":228337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:18:32.000Z","msg":"我未過P<br />\n只能請VL，請ed <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6aa5e86c25c421260324f67b5a923a33789512","tid":1395002,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:20:02.000Z","msg":"公務員都冇isp email<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee70903ee0cf44741362fdfd6bbda97ba03311d9","tid":1395002,"uid":882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:20:13.000Z","msg":"塞路 大條道理拎time off"},{"pid":"bde9104f8bcd4cb4583ac33ceda71380bc2af416","tid":1395002,"uid":107686,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"唔同意<br />\n一尼8.5有集會遊行<br />\n二尼做不合作運動即係話唔會知道幾多人真心支持罷工=冇說服力"},{"pid":"892289dd4ecb1f8e18e5e1ca87d29426f5508ff8","tid":1395002,"uid":294896,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"感覺有啲伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d4cec8b49e5b685f27c2fec9be55031ec7d36a","tid":1395002,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bde9104f8bcd4cb4583ac33ceda71380bc2af416","tid":1395002,"uid":107686,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"唔同意<br />\n一尼8.5有集會遊行<br />\n二尼做不合作運動即係話唔會知道幾多人真心支持罷工=冇說服力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"再遊行既成效有幾多？"},{"pid":"0421523aa20c6f7c910bb3133404649d9639b74d","tid":1395002,"uid":65790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:23:10.000Z","msg":"支持不合作運動<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">交通燈，過海隧道，迴旋處，快閃佔路，塞鐵，巴士按章工作，機場集會</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"67ce6f0c01e35d89b5600cd0758546302eed5f76","tid":1395002,"uid":143526,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"求下你地"},{"pid":"0b8563663ef657a8ca4ce01299a6df3edc77597e","tid":1395002,"uid":107686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bde9104f8bcd4cb4583ac33ceda71380bc2af416","tid":1395002,"uid":107686,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"唔同意<br />\n一尼8.5有集會遊行<br />\n二尼做不合作運動即係話唔會知道幾多人真心支持罷工=冇說服力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:24:00.000Z","msg":"不合作運動 同話比中間派知冇人支持罷工 冇分別<br />\n罷工唔係只睇8.5 如果係多人既話 完全可以擴大成果 爭取 更多人 更長時間 既罷工"},{"pid":"aac2baa2c21348f264f53374ef6734b7df1a94f5","tid":1395002,"uid":21253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"probation唔禁罷都都拎左AL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1646e139db149f6e12b6b058cfbb9a423cf49e3","tid":1395002,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"公務員就算唔罷工，都可以按章工作"},{"pid":"31cd97a166e901dcf7a7143f09a0521b08365908","tid":1395002,"uid":21253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aac2baa2c21348f264f53374ef6734b7df1a94f5","tid":1395002,"uid":21253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"probation唔禁罷都都拎左AL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:24:51.000Z","msg":"禁-&gt;敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b18562a3d393b2a2c6086153fba29d886815122","tid":1395002,"uid":32586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c6aa5e86c25c421260324f67b5a923a33789512","tid":1395002,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:20:02.000Z","msg":"公務員都冇isp email<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:25:03.000Z","msg":"個isp開唔到連登ac"},{"pid":"d4e0e531c0fb1e5910744b68e4e678b781ae8bb0","tid":1395002,"uid":21253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8dcf47a4330f2f18fdafd45a46be80c57bed6d","tid":1395002,"uid":18948,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:28:53.000Z","msg":"消防，當值，我做好自己本分就係對你地最大嘅支持，如果當日我架車經過我會響號開咪支持你哋"},{"pid":"52860906db10e6c40afa6a9c7cb1a845886f84b9","tid":1395002,"uid":260335,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:31:17.000Z","msg":"再遊行 再衝擊 再受傷 再被捕 <br />\n國際壓力我地贏左 但成效？<br />\n登報贏左 成效？ <br />\n衝入立法會 街頭抗爭 成效？<br />\n<br />\n我地已經失去過百位義士<br />\n再遊行 再集會 意義係有 但唔會有成效<br />\n<br />\n今次8月5 以可話係最後一戰"},{"pid":"3258290823ab882c5614fa4cff385208f200a749","tid":1395002,"uid":61974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:31:52.000Z","msg":"不要說：「要返工，不了。」 試著說：「要罷工，不了。」"},{"pid":"60ecaeecafde6c9ab7ade718aa8e7b59a093f126","tid":1395002,"uid":105861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:32:08.000Z","msg":"屯元天搞緊大西北不合作運動，110萬人無得坐西鐵就大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無北區大埔沙田手足唔好係大圍/九龍塘火車站唔小心跌野，3區人口120萬，係得坐火車出黎就大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>[遍地開花］8月5朝早7點15元朗西鐵站要屯元天人！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391481</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a6ae4811dc05dcccbaada5fbfade97a0e210aa86","tid":1395002,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:32:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53ad829de525c05b593db1e4aa180321a22e07b2","tid":1395002,"uid":105861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:34:29.000Z","msg":"如果200萬人無得坐鐵出市區咁除左返沙田大埔同屯門七區集會仲有咩做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d3744335f5fd3fbe9cb38eb2600d540746510a","tid":1395002,"uid":58669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a09c115c93672cf7857581d98dbb08fda1e43ad","tid":1395002,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:41:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4348212ab93137925c2c4bbcf1d7684198ba54af","tid":1395002,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:42:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"839b23183f7ce926dd10b749874b4dfd20ac13e7","tid":1395002,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:46:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47031ff453d7ff3781e164bf0698b07b95f0c55b","tid":1395002,"uid":263798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:48:31.000Z","msg":"推！！<br />\n身邊好多朋友都係心想罷工但操作上真係有困難<br />\n如果名正言順被迫罷工，相信有好多人會支持！<br />\n<br />\n除左地鐵之外，路面不合作運動真係唔少得<br />\n尤其係一啲交叉位，或平時返工必經路，效果更佳(對上幾次效果一般)<br />\ne.g.屯公、屯公駁下路回旋處、汀九、青馬、龍翔道，etc<br />\n<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！"},{"pid":"1135ac20df0b7cfceb1a915b9c6207a5bcd89cf1","tid":1395002,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:49:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00002bf974da23535dc0129555b77b64fa65fd0b","tid":1395002,"uid":105861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油呀公墓猿"},{"pid":"60e3b0a7decce34fa7b88bf9c1bdd3beca15456f","tid":1395002,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:02:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e29dc57f68bc6b72ef518ade8f666c39c59ccb9","tid":1395002,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:22:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17f836f09a8ec9ef97b15691dda446d9134b7a9d","tid":1395002,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:26:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74c190a4f0218aec8827690ae2e59